{
"#useparam"
:
true
,
"#name"
:
{
"x feishu"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"使用飞书群机器人发送消息"
,
"en"
:
"Send messages using a Feishu group bot"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 x feishu 向你的飞书群发送消息。首次使用需要配置 webhook url。"
,
"en"
:
"Use x feishu send messages to your Feishu. The first use requires configuring webhook url."
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Instructions for get the webhook url for Feishu group bot: https://open.feishu.cn/document/client-docs/bot-v3/add-custom-bot#7a28964d\n- Interactive env use `x feishu init` to initialize configuration. The configure will be saved locally.\n- Run command `x feishu --cfg webhook=<webhook_url>` to add webhook url.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"飞书群机器人 webhook url 获取指引: https://open.feishu.cn/document/client-docs/bot-v3/add-custom-bot#7a28964d\n- 交互环境中可使用 `x feishu init` 进行初始化配置，配置信息将存放于本地保存\n- 亦可运行命令 `x feishu --cfg webhook=<webhook_url>` 添加 webhook url\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu --cfg webhook=<webhook>"
,
"cn"
:
"设置 webhook url"
,
"en"
:
"set webhook url"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu send --text \"x-cmd 新版本发布成功\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到飞书群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Feishu group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu send --richtext   \\\n  --title \"Demo of Feishu\" \\\n  --text \"Welcome to x-cmd's website for details:\" \\\n  --url \"website\" \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\"\n"
,
"cn"
:
"发送一个标题为 \"Demo of Feishu\"，链接到 \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\" 的消息"
,
"en"
:
"A message with the title \"Demo of Feishu\" will be sent, linking to \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\""
}
]
,
"#subcmd:config"
:
[
"init"
,
"--cfg"
,
"--cur"
]
,
"send"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用飞书群机器人发送消息（等同于 x feishu bot send）"
,
"en"
:
"Send messages using a Feishu group bot (equivalent to `x feishu bot send`)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu send --text \"x-cmd 新版本发布成功\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到飞书群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Feishu group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu send --richtext   \\\n  --title \"Demo of Feishu\" \\\n  --text \"Welcome to x-cmd's website for details:\" \\\n  --url \"website\" \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\"\n"
,
"cn"
:
"发送一个标题为 \"Demo of Feishu\"，链接到 \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\" 的消息"
,
"en"
:
"A message with the title \"Demo of Feishu\" will be sent, linking to \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\""
}
]
,
"--raw"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"发送原始的 JSON 数据"
,
"en"
:
"send raw json"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu send --raw - <<A\n  {\n      \"msgtype\": \"text\",\n      \"text\": {\n          \"content\": \"<content>\"\n      }\n  }\n  A"
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到飞书群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Feishu group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"cat markdown.json | x feishu send --raw -"
,
"cn"
:
"从文件中读取 JSON 数据并发送消息"
,
"en"
:
"Reading JSON data from a file and sending a message"
}
]
,
"--json|-j"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in Json format"
}
}
,
"--webhook"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定群机器人发送消息所用的 webhook"
,
"en"
:
"The webhook used by the specified group of bots to send messages"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"发送的原始 JSON 消息内容，可以使用 \"-\" 从标准输入读取 JSON 数据"
,
"en"
:
"The original JSON message content that was sent. You can read JSON data from standard input using \"-\""
}
}
}
,
