"react"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用飞书群机器人接受信息，并使用机器人向群内发送命令执行的结果。注意需要先行配置飞书群机器人，并将 \"获取群组信息\",\"获取与更新群组信息\",\"查看群信息\",\"获取单聊、群组消息\"权限授予机器人。"
,
"en"
:
"Use a Feishu group bot to receive messages and send the command execution results back to the group via the bot. Note that you need to configure the Feishu group bot first, and grant the bot the following permissions \"Obtain group information\", \"Obtain and update group information\", \"View group information\", and \"Obtain single chat and group messages\"."
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu bot react echo 'x-cmd feishu bot'"
,
"cn"
:
"接受群内消息，并将```echo 'x-cmd feishu bot'``` 执行的结果发送到该群内"
,
"en"
:
"Receive messages from the group and send the execution result of echo 'x-cmd feishu bot' back to the group."
}
]
}
}
,
"init"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Initialize the configuration using interactive mode"
,
"cn"
:
"使用交互模式初始化配置"
}
}
,
"--cur"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"current session default value management"
,
"cn"
:
"当前会话默认值管理"
}
,
"clear"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Clear all setting default in the current session and reback the default value of the config record"
,
"cn"
:
"清除当前会话设置的默认值, 恢复为配置记录默认值"
}
}
,
"ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"List all current value in the session"
,
"cn"
:
"罗列当前会话设置的所有默认值"
}
}
}
,
"--cfg"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"manage configuration for Feishu"
,
"cn"
:
"飞书配置管理"
}
,
"#tip:note"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Instructions for get the webhook url for Feishu group bot: https://open.feishu.cn/document/client-docs/bot-v3/add-custom-bot#7a28964d\n"
,
"cn"
:
"飞书群机器人 webhook url 获取指引: https://open.feishu.cn/document/client-docs/bot-v3/add-custom-bot#7a28964d\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu --cfg webhook=<webhook_url>"
,
"en"
:
"Setup webhook url for default initialization"
,
"cn"
:
"添加 webhook url, 进行默认初始化"
}
]
,
"set"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Setting Feishu config"
,
"cn"
:
"设置飞书配置"
}
,
"--config"
:
{
